{"contest": {"title": "", "missionTitle": "콘테스트에 참가해서 함께 즐기자！", "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"support-card support-card--wide\"><div class=\"support-top-stripe\"></div><div class=\"support-inner\">\n\n<style>\n/* ── 콘테스트ページ専用スタイル ── */\n.ct-page-header {\n  text-align: center;\n  padding: 8px 0 32px;\n}\n.ct-page-title {\n  font-family: 'Kaisei Tokumin', serif;\n  font-size: 2em;\n  font-weight: 900;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff79b0 0%, #c084fc 100%);\n  -webkit-background-clip: text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n  background-clip: text;\n  margin-bottom: 6px;\n}\n.ct-page-sub {\n  font-size: .9em;\n  color: var(--muted);\n  letter-spacing: .06em;\n}\n\n/* ── アクティブ콘테스트カード ── */\n.ct-active-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n  grid-template-rows: auto auto;\n  gap: 20px;\n  margin-bottom: 40px;\n  align-items: start;\n}\n@media(max-width:700px){.ct-active-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}\n\n.ct-contest-card {\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.2);\n  border-radius: 24px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,.02);\n  transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;\n  cursor: pointer;\n}\n.ct-contest-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-3px);\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255,121,176,.15);\n}\n.ct-contest-card[open] {\n  cursor: default;\n  transform: none;\n}\n.ct-contest-card summary {\n  list-style: none;\n  outline: none;\n}\n.ct-contest-card summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }\n\n.ct-card-thumb {\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,.2);\n}\n.ct-card-thumb img {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: auto;\n  max-height: 320px;\n  object-fit: contain;\n  object-position: top center;\n  display: block;\n  transition: transform .3s;\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,.2);\n}\n.ct-contest-card:not([open]) .ct-card-thumb img:hover {\n  transform: scale(1.03);\n}\n.ct-card-badge {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 12px;\n  right: 12px;\n  padding: 4px 12px;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  font-size: .75em;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(6px);\n}\n.ct-card-badge--pink {\n  background: rgba(255,121,176,.85);\n  color: #fff;\n}\n.ct-card-badge--blue {\n  background: rgba(96,165,250,.85);\n  color: #fff;\n}\n.ct-card-badge--teal {\n  background: rgba(45,212,191,.85);\n  color: #fff;\n}\n\n.ct-card-body {\n  padding: 18px 20px 20px;\n}\n.ct-card-title {\n  font-family: 'Kaisei Tokumin', serif;\n  font-size: 1.1em;\n  font-weight: 900;\n  margin-bottom: 4px;\n  color: var(--text);\n}\n.ct-card-deadline {\n  font-size: .78em;\n  color: var(--muted);\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n.ct-card-desc {\n  font-size: .85em;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,.75);\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n}\n.ct-card-tags {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 6px;\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n}\n.ct-card-tag {\n  padding: 3px 10px;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  font-size: .75em;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.3);\n  color: var(--accent);\n  background: rgba(255,121,176,.07);\n}\n.ct-card-actions {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 8px;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n.ct-card-btn {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 6px;\n  padding: 8px 16px;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  font-size: .82em;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  transition: opacity .15s, transform .1s;\n  border: none;\n  cursor: pointer;\n}\n.ct-card-btn:hover { opacity: .85; transform: translateY(-1px); }\n.ct-card-btn--primary {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff79b0, #c084fc);\n  color: #fff;\n}\n.ct-card-btn--secondary {\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);\n  color: var(--text);\n}\n\n/* オニギリスライダー（カード内） */\n.ct-onigiri-slider { position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 0; }\n.ct-onigiri-track { display: flex; transition: transform .3s ease; }\n.ct-onigiri-slide { min-width: 100%; flex-shrink: 0; }\n.ct-onigiri-slide img { width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 320px; object-fit: contain; object-position: top; display: block; background: rgba(0,0,0,.2); }\n.ct-onigiri-nav {\n  position: absolute; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);\n  width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,.6); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);\n  color: #fff; cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px;\n  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n  z-index: 5;\n}\n.ct-onigiri-nav--prev { left: 8px; }\n.ct-onigiri-nav--next { right: 8px; }\n.ct-onigiri-dots { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; padding: 10px 0 0; }\n.ct-onigiri-dot {\n  width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;\n  background: var(--accent); border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0;\n  opacity: .3; transition: opacity .2s;\n}\n.ct-onigiri-dot.active { opacity: 1; }\n\n/* ── 지난 콘테스트 ── */\n.ct-archive-section { margin-top: 48px; }\n.ct-archive-title {\n  font-size: 1.4em;\n  font-family: 'Kaisei Tokumin', serif;\n  font-weight: 900;\n  color: var(--accent);\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n  padding-bottom: 12px;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.2);\n}\n.ct-archive-card {\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,.02);\n}\n.ct-archive-summary {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 14px;\n  padding: 14px 18px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  user-select: none;\n}\n.ct-archive-summary { list-style: none; }\n.ct-archive-summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }\n.ct-archive-summary::marker { display: none; }\n.ct-archive-icon {\n  width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 12px;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);\n  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n  font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n.ct-archive-info { flex: 1; }\n.ct-archive-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: .95em; }\n.ct-archive-period { font-size: .78em; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }\n.ct-archive-arrow {\n  font-size: .8em; color: var(--muted);\n  transition: transform .2s;\n}\ndetails.ct-archive-card[open] .ct-archive-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }\n.ct-archive-inner { padding: 0 18px 20px; }\n\n/* 受賞作品グリッド */\n.ct-awards-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n  gap: 14px;\n  margin-bottom: 16px;\n}\n@media(max-width:500px){.ct-awards-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}\n.ct-award-item { text-align: center; }\n.ct-award-label {\n  display: inline-block;\n  padding: 3px 12px;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  font-size: .75em;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin-bottom: 6px;\n}\n.ct-award-label--gold { background: rgba(255,200,50,.15); color: #fde68a; border: 1px solid rgba(255,200,50,.3); }\n.ct-award-label--silver { background: rgba(180,180,220,.1); color: #c0c0e0; border: 1px solid rgba(180,180,220,.25); }\n.ct-award-name { font-size: .85em; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }\n.ct-award-img {\n  width: 100%; max-width: 280px;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.4);\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: transform .2s;\n}\n.ct-award-img:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }\n\n/* アニメーション */\n@keyframes ct-fade-up {\n  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }\n  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n}\n.ct-contest-card {\n  animation: ct-fade-up .4s ease both;\n}\n.ct-contest-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: .08s; }\n.ct-contest-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: .16s; }\n\n/* ── 詳細（開閉）エリア ── */\n.ct-card-more {\n  margin-top: 10px;\n  font-size: .78em;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: var(--accent);\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.ct-contest-card[open] .ct-card-more { display: none; }\n.ct-card-detail {\n  padding: 4px 20px 22px;\n  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.15);\n  margin-top: 4px;\n  animation: ct-fade-up .3s ease both;\n}\n.ct-detail-lead {\n  font-size: .88em;\n  line-height: 1.8;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,.85);\n  margin: 16px 0 18px;\n}\n.ct-detail-section { margin-bottom: 16px; }\n.ct-detail-heading {\n  font-weight: 900;\n  font-size: .92em;\n  color: var(--accent);\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n.ct-detail-list {\n  margin: 0;\n  padding-left: 1.3em;\n  font-size: .85em;\n  line-height: 1.9;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);\n}\n.ct-detail-list li { margin-bottom: 2px; }\n.ct-detail-text {\n  font-size: .85em;\n  line-height: 1.9;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);\n}\n</style>\n\n<!-- ヘッダー -->\n<div class=\"ct-page-header\">\n  <div class=\"ct-page-title\">콘테스트</div>\n  <div class=\"ct-page-sub\">콘테스트에 참가하고 고조하자!</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- ===== アクティブ콘테스트 ===== -->\n<div class=\"ct-active-grid\">\n\n  <!-- 御手洗THEサマーイラコン -->\n  <details class=\"ct-contest-card\">\n    <summary>\n      <div class=\"ct-card-thumb\">\n        <img src=\"./assets/御手洗THEサマーイラコン.png\" alt=\"미타라이 THE 서머 일러스트 콘테스트\"\n          onerror=\"this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\"\n          onclick=\"openLightbox('./assets/御手洗THEサマーイラコン.png');event.stopPropagation()\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:auto;max-height:320px;object-fit:contain;display:block;background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);cursor:zoom-in;\" />\n        <div style=\"display:none;width:100%;height:180px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,200,50,.15),rgba(255,121,176,.15));align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:4em;\">🌻</div>\n        <span class=\"ct-card-badge ct-card-badge--blue\">📅 8월 13일 마감</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ct-card-body\">\n        <div class=\"ct-card-title\">☀️ 미타라이 THE 서머 일러스트 콘테스트</div>\n        <div class=\"ct-card-deadline\">마감：8월 13일 (목)</div>\n        <div class=\"ct-card-desc\">일러스트 콘테스트가 드디어 시작됩니다! 여름의 미타라이 아소부를 그려 보세요! 의상과 헤어스타일은 자유, 상상력을 마음껏 펼쳐 주세요~ 🤍</div>\n        <div class=\"ct-card-more\">▼ 탭해서 자세히 보기</div>\n      </div>\n    </summary>\n    <div class=\"ct-card-detail\">\n      <div class=\"ct-detail-lead\">\n        미타라이 THE 서머 ☀🌊<br>\n        일러스트 콘테스트가 드디어 시작됩니다!<br>\n        여름의 미타라이 아소부를 그려 보세요!<br>\n        의상과 헤어스타일은 자유! 상상력을 마음껏 펼쳐 주세요~ 🤍<br>\n        X에 #미타라이THE서머 해시태그를 달아 게시해 주세요!\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ct-detail-section\">\n        <div class=\"ct-detail-heading\">🏅 수상 부문</div>\n        <ul class=\"ct-detail-list\">\n          <li>등신 일러스트상</li>\n          <li>SD(미니 캐릭터)상</li>\n          <li>특별상 (아이디어나 재미를 높게 평가하는 부문)</li>\n          <li>애니메이션상</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ct-detail-section\">\n        <div class=\"ct-detail-heading\">📝 응모 자격</div>\n        <ul class=\"ct-detail-list\">\n          <li>채색이 완료된 작품일 것</li>\n          <li>배꼽 위까지 그려져 있을 것</li>\n          <li>이미지 크기는 1000×1000px 이상일 것</li>\n          <li>전체 이용가 작품일 것</li>\n          <li>오리지널 의상·헤어스타일 가능</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ct-detail-section\">\n        <div class=\"ct-detail-heading\">⏰ 응모 마감</div>\n        <div class=\"ct-detail-text\">8월 13일 (목)</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ct-detail-section\">\n        <div class=\"ct-detail-heading\">🎁 상품</div>\n        <div class=\"ct-detail-text\">멤버십 1개월권 또는 굿즈 1개</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ct-detail-section\">\n        <div class=\"ct-detail-heading\">⚠️ 주의사항</div>\n        <div class=\"ct-detail-text\">\n          굿즈를 받으시려면 주소와 성함을 제공해 주셔야 합니다.<br>\n          응모 작품은 적극적으로 활용될 예정이며, 굿즈나 스티커 등 상업적으로 사용될 수 있습니다.<br>\n          콘테스트에 참가하는 시점에 위 내용에 동의한 것으로 간주됩니다.<br>\n          AI로 생성한 일러스트는 참가할 수 없습니다.<br>\n          실력이 부족하다고 느끼더라도 직접 그려 주신다면 정말 기쁠 것 같아요!\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ct-card-actions\">\n        <a href=\"https://x.com/hashtag/%E5%BE%A1%E6%89%8B%E6%B4%97THE%E3%82%B5%E3%83%9E%E3%83%BC?src=hashtag_click&f=live\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"ct-card-btn ct-card-btn--primary\">👀 모두의 작품 보기</a>\n        <a href=\"./assets/御手洗THEサマーイラコン.png\" download class=\"ct-card-btn ct-card-btn--secondary\">⬇ 이미지 다운로드</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </details>\n\n  <!-- オニギリラクーン콘테스트 -->\n  <div class=\"ct-contest-card\">\n      <div c